Detailed Description

Common data structures used by IonicSDK modules.

Classes:
DeviceProfile - Data class for storing device profile information (a.k.a. SEP data).
DeviceProfileList - List of DeviceProfiles.
DeviceProfilePersistorBase - Abstract class used to load and save device profiles.
DeviceProfilePersistorAesGcmFile - Key protected file persistor.
DeviceProfilePersistorDefault - Platform default persistor.
DeviceProfilePersistorPasswordFile - Password protected file persistor.
DeviceProfilePersistorPlaintextFile - Unprotected file persistor.
KeyAttributesDict - Default Dictionary of string Attribute names with lists of string values.
KeyData - Defines a data protection key as returned by Ionic.com.
KeyDataList - List of KeyData with search functionality.
MetadataDict - Dictionary of string to string data sent along with HTTP requests.
